{"tha-ap280:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap280:0.2":"Suvannabibbohanavagga ","tha-ap280:0.3":"Aluvadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap280:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap280:1.2":"mahasindhu sudassana; ","tha-ap280:1.3":"Tatthaddasam vitaragam, ","tha-ap280:1.4":"suppabhasam sudassanam. ","tha-ap280:2.1":"Paramopasame yuttam, ","tha-ap280:2.2":"disva vimhitamanaso; ","tha-ap280:2.3":"Aluvam tassa padasim, ","tha-ap280:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap280:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap280:3.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap280:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap280:3.4":"aluvassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap280:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap280:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap280:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap280:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma aluvadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap280:6.1":"Aluvadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}